1
00:00:07,290 --> 00:00:08,450
<font color="yellow">A man...</font>

2
00:00:09,390 --> 00:00:11,120
<font color="yellow">fell in love three times.</font>

3
00:00:12,090 --> 00:00:14,420
<font color="yellow">Would you believe it if I said it was with the same woman?</font>

4
00:00:17,020 --> 00:00:18,650
<font color="yellow">The first time,</font>

5
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:21,990
<font color="yellow">the man was unable to see.</font>

6
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:26,090
<font color="yellow">Ten years later...</font>

7
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:29,620
<font color="yellow">when he met her again after regaining his sight,</font>

8
00:00:31,790 --> 00:00:33,950
<font color="yellow">he didn't know she was the one he was looking for.</font>

9
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:36,950
<font color="yellow">And he fell in love again.</font>

10
00:00:39,390 --> 00:00:40,620
<font color="yellow">Then the man...</font>

11
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,820
<font color="yellow">lost his memory.</font>

12
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:48,950
<font color="yellow">Being the fool he was,</font>

13
00:00:50,450 --> 00:00:52,750
<font color="yellow">he fell in love with her again.</font>

14
00:01:02,250 --> 00:01:03,290
<font color="yellow">Jeong Eun.</font>

15
00:01:06,290 --> 00:01:07,320
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

16
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:14,650
<font color="yellow">This is the third time.</font>

17
00:01:16,890 --> 00:01:18,220
<font color="yellow">Even if I die,</font>

18
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:21,150
<font color="yellow">I won't lose you again.</font>

19
00:01:29,490 --> 00:01:30,950
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon, no. Soo Yeon.</font>

20
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:35,620
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon. No. Don't die, Soo Yeon.</font>

21
00:01:35,620 --> 00:01:37,710
<font color="yellow">I found the evidence of Il Jae's corruption.</font>

22
00:01:37,710 --> 00:01:38,720
<font color="yellow">Who are you people?</font>

23
00:01:40,620 --> 00:01:41,620
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

24
00:01:42,250 --> 00:01:43,920
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, stay with me.</font>

25
00:01:44,790 --> 00:01:48,190
<font color="yellow">Help! We need help!</font>

26
00:01:48,190 --> 00:01:49,420
<font color="yellow">Let's get engaged.</font>

27
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:51,920
<font color="yellow">Before your father passes.</font>

28
00:01:53,420 --> 00:01:54,420
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

29
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,120
<font color="yellow">I took too long to answer.</font>

30
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:11,790
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Gi Tan.</font>

31
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,590
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo...</font>

32
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:20,320
<font color="yellow">helped me a lot thus far.</font>

33
00:02:22,260 --> 00:02:23,850
<font color="yellow">I can't selfishly hope to be happy...</font>

34
00:02:25,450 --> 00:02:26,820
<font color="yellow">after abandoning Gun Woo.</font>

35
00:02:28,790 --> 00:02:30,820
<font color="yellow">Jeong Eun, Gun Woo is...</font>

36
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:32,150
<font color="yellow">Once I get my revenge on Il Jae,</font>

37
00:02:33,790 --> 00:02:35,190
<font color="yellow">I will never see you again.</font>

38
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:43,420
<font color="yellow">I do not...</font>

39
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,290
<font color="yellow">love you any more.</font>

40
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,350
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Gi Tan.</font>

41
00:03:38,820 --> 00:03:39,820
<font color="yellow">(Episode 43)</font>

42
00:03:55,390 --> 00:03:56,750
<font color="yellow">Nan Jeong told me...</font>

43
00:03:57,790 --> 00:04:00,190
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon will get engaged to Gun Woo soon.</font>

44
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:03,490
<font color="yellow">I should have stopped him from meeting Lawyer Oh yesterday.</font>

45
00:04:03,490 --> 00:04:06,120
<font color="yellow">I'm worried that he might get his headache back.</font>

46
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,120
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

47
00:04:20,790 --> 00:04:23,320
<font color="yellow">What happened to getting the agreement from the creditors?</font>

48
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:26,250
<font color="yellow">Here they are.</font>

49
00:04:28,290 --> 00:04:29,820
<font color="yellow">(Creditors' Agreement)</font>

50
00:04:29,820 --> 00:04:31,700
<font color="yellow">What about the contract we'll enter with Dodo Group?</font>

51
00:04:31,700 --> 00:04:32,890
<font color="yellow">It's all ready.</font>

52
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:34,420
<font color="yellow">Tell Gun Woo...</font>

53
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,250
<font color="yellow">to come to the hotel.</font>

54
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:37,620
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

55
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:39,390
<font color="yellow">(Dodo Group)</font>

56
00:04:44,650 --> 00:04:45,790
<font color="yellow">(Moon Tae Gwang)</font>

57
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,520
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

58
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,620
<font color="yellow">The chairman wants to meet you.</font>

59
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:56,690
<font color="yellow">You can come to my office at 1pm.</font>

60
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:00,060
<font color="yellow">Come to the hotel.</font>

61
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:03,420
<font color="yellow">I have no time to go over.</font>

62
00:05:04,790 --> 00:05:07,650
<font color="yellow">If you don't come here by 1pm, the meeting will be cancelled.</font>

63
00:05:10,590 --> 00:05:13,060
<font color="yellow">He wants us to come to his office.</font>

64
00:05:19,250 --> 00:05:21,990
<font color="yellow">Do not change the holding company to Dodo Hotel.</font>

65
00:05:23,290 --> 00:05:26,090
<font color="yellow">In that case, Gi Tan will take out all of the bonds.</font>

66
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,350
<font color="yellow">Tell him to do that.</font>

67
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,490
<font color="yellow">If he does,</font>

68
00:05:31,490 --> 00:05:33,850
<font color="yellow">we cannot run Dodo Group with the capital we have.</font>

69
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:35,790
<font color="yellow">I have...</font>

70
00:05:36,350 --> 00:05:37,890
<font color="yellow">an idea, Gun Woo.</font>

71
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:45,490
<font color="yellow">I'll...</font>

72
00:05:47,090 --> 00:05:48,830
<font color="yellow">help you with the expiring bonds.</font>

73
00:05:50,130 --> 00:05:52,060
<font color="yellow">It's over 500 million dollars.</font>

74
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:54,860
<font color="yellow">We only have 200 million in Z Capital.</font>

75
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:57,730
<font color="yellow">Of course it won't be enough with what I have.</font>

76
00:05:57,730 --> 00:05:59,950
<font color="yellow">However, we can get a loan...</font>

77
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:02,730
<font color="yellow">from Z Capital with what I have as security.</font>

78
00:06:03,290 --> 00:06:05,690
<font color="yellow">I've already discussed it with them.</font>

79
00:06:06,790 --> 00:06:09,360
<font color="yellow">I have a condition in return for helping you.</font>

80
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:12,630
<font color="yellow">Break the joint account.</font>

81
00:06:22,730 --> 00:06:23,930
<font color="yellow">I have a condition as well.</font>

82
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:30,110
<font color="yellow">I don't think you're in the position to demand conditions.</font>

83
00:06:30,110 --> 00:06:32,160
<font color="yellow">No, I told you.</font>

84
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,990
<font color="yellow">I came empty-handed when I moved here from the US.</font>

85
00:06:34,430 --> 00:06:37,590
<font color="yellow">At the worst, I can just go back empty-handed again.</font>

86
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:46,490
<font color="yellow">All right. Go ahead and tell me.</font>

87
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:47,890
<font color="yellow">I'm...</font>

88
00:06:48,530 --> 00:06:50,060
<font color="yellow">going to get engaged to Soo Yeon.</font>

89
00:06:51,690 --> 00:06:54,430
<font color="yellow">Please don't interfere in our relationship any more.</font>

90
00:06:57,590 --> 00:06:59,930
<font color="yellow">All right. I won't.</font>

91
00:07:10,990 --> 00:07:13,590
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon, can you come to my office right now?</font>

92
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:22,230
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo must be confused.</font>

93
00:07:22,590 --> 00:07:24,130
<font color="yellow">He should have come running to us.</font>

94
00:07:24,130 --> 00:07:26,690
<font color="yellow">How dare he tell us to come here?</font>

95
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:38,060
<font color="yellow">Did something happen yesterday?</font>

96
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:41,580
<font color="yellow">What? Why?</font>

97
00:07:41,580 --> 00:07:45,290
<font color="yellow">You didn't pick up your phone and you look down today.</font>

98
00:07:46,090 --> 00:07:47,460
<font color="yellow">I'm just tired.</font>

99
00:07:48,130 --> 00:07:49,430
<font color="yellow">It's fine.</font>

100
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:51,290
<font color="yellow">I shouldn't have asked you to come.</font>

101
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:54,990
<font color="yellow">I'm your legal counsel. Of course I should be here.</font>

102
00:08:01,290 --> 00:08:02,830
<font color="yellow">Chairman Kang is here.</font>

103
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:04,690
<font color="yellow">- Show them in.
-  Yes, Sir.</font>

104
00:08:20,890 --> 00:08:21,930
<font color="yellow">Take a seat.</font>

105
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,430
<font color="yellow">I don't have time, so let's get to the point.</font>

106
00:08:32,230 --> 00:08:33,230
<font color="yellow">Mr Moon.</font>

107
00:08:34,990 --> 00:08:36,730
<font color="yellow">Here are the consent forms from the creditors.</font>

108
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,360
<font color="yellow">If you want to renew the bonds,</font>

109
00:08:47,290 --> 00:08:48,960
<font color="yellow">switch your holding company to Dodo Hotel.</font>

110
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,290
<font color="yellow">You're a coward.</font>

111
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,190
<font color="yellow">How can you set me in a trap...</font>

112
00:08:52,190 --> 00:08:54,330
<font color="yellow">with the ship contract to win over Dodo Group?</font>

113
00:08:54,330 --> 00:08:56,160
<font color="yellow">You better talk properly.</font>

114
00:08:56,760 --> 00:09:00,590
<font color="yellow">You're the coward for turning Gi Tan into a murderer.</font>

115
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,460
<font color="yellow">To me,</font>

116
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:07,290
<font color="yellow">there were no problems with the way Gi Tan did his business.</font>

117
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:10,090
<font color="yellow">It's your greed that set you in that trap.</font>

118
00:09:10,530 --> 00:09:13,290
<font color="yellow">You must be brainwashed after sticking by Gi Tan's side.</font>

119
00:09:13,290 --> 00:09:14,990
<font color="yellow">Enough with that nonsense.</font>

120
00:09:15,490 --> 00:09:18,230
<font color="yellow">Just change the holding company to Dodo Hotel right now.</font>

121
00:09:18,730 --> 00:09:20,690
<font color="yellow">Otherwise, it's over for you.</font>

122
00:09:20,690 --> 00:09:24,560
<font color="yellow">Here is a memorandum to state that you will switch to Dodo Hotel.</font>

123
00:09:26,430 --> 00:09:27,630
<font color="yellow">Please sign it.</font>

124
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:31,560
<font color="yellow">If you don't sign it now,</font>

125
00:09:32,390 --> 00:09:34,430
<font color="yellow">we won't be renewing the bonds.</font>

126
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:37,360
<font color="yellow">Think wisely.</font>

127
00:09:51,990 --> 00:09:53,190
<font color="yellow">Do as you wish.</font>

128
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:56,160
<font color="yellow">I'll use my own money if I have to.</font>

129
00:09:57,190 --> 00:09:58,830
<font color="yellow">You don't have any money.</font>

130
00:09:59,430 --> 00:10:01,860
<font color="yellow">Oh, are you referring to Dad's inheritance?</font>

131
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:04,830
<font color="yellow">Do you think you'll get that money in six months?</font>

132
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:06,560
<font color="yellow">You better wake up.</font>

133
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,790
<font color="yellow">Don't regret it later after losing everything to Gi Tan.</font>

134
00:10:09,660 --> 00:10:10,660
<font color="yellow">Are you...</font>

135
00:10:12,060 --> 00:10:13,990
<font color="yellow">getting help from Byun Il Jae?</font>

136
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:19,050
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

137
00:10:19,050 --> 00:10:21,360
<font color="yellow">We're tracking his financial movements.</font>

138
00:10:22,490 --> 00:10:26,030
<font color="yellow">I noticed that all the money he had in his paper company disappeared.</font>

139
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:30,970
<font color="yellow">Are you still making up stories?</font>

140
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:32,060
<font color="yellow">I do hope...</font>

141
00:10:33,230 --> 00:10:35,250
<font color="yellow">it's just my imagination.</font>

142
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:37,330
<font color="yellow">Imagine all you want,</font>

143
00:10:37,930 --> 00:10:40,290
<font color="yellow">but give up on your dream to take over Dodo Group.</font>

144
00:10:40,690 --> 00:10:42,460
<font color="yellow">I won't let that happen.</font>

145
00:10:42,460 --> 00:10:44,760
<font color="yellow">I don't care what strategy you use,</font>

146
00:10:47,190 --> 00:10:49,190
<font color="yellow">but don't get Il Jae's help.</font>

147
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:51,190
<font color="yellow">You should think about Soo Yeon.</font>

148
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:55,160
<font color="yellow">It would be inhumane.</font>

149
00:11:00,430 --> 00:11:03,160
<font color="yellow">The negotiation fell apart, Sir. Let's go.</font>

150
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:12,620
<font color="yellow">He definitely has something to rely on.</font>

151
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:15,330
<font color="yellow">He wouldn't have ripped those documents like that if he didn't.</font>

152
00:11:15,330 --> 00:11:18,460
<font color="yellow">Once those bonds expire, the company will be ruined.</font>

153
00:11:18,460 --> 00:11:19,690
<font color="yellow">When will we know...</font>

154
00:11:20,260 --> 00:11:21,660
<font color="yellow">about Il Jae's finances?</font>

155
00:11:21,660 --> 00:11:24,330
<font color="yellow">He's very meticulous so it's hard to track.</font>

156
00:11:24,890 --> 00:11:27,160
<font color="yellow">But do you really think...</font>

157
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:29,690
<font color="yellow">Il Jae is helping Gun Woo?</font>

158
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:31,530
<font color="yellow">I believe it's quite possible...</font>

159
00:11:32,130 --> 00:11:33,890
<font color="yellow">also since Hwang Jae Man helped us.</font>

160
00:11:35,060 --> 00:11:37,030
<font color="yellow">Why don't we contact Yeom Hyeong Gu?</font>

161
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:39,630
<font color="yellow">It might be faster that way.</font>

162
00:11:40,030 --> 00:11:42,330
<font color="yellow">- Go and meet with him.
-  Yes, Sir.</font>

163
00:12:08,930 --> 00:12:10,690
<font color="yellow">I saw Gi Tan on my way in.</font>

164
00:12:13,130 --> 00:12:16,530
<font color="yellow">It was funny to see them all confused.</font>

165
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:35,060
<font color="yellow">It's the termination agreement on our joint account.</font>

166
00:12:38,460 --> 00:12:40,090
<font color="yellow">(Joint Account Termination Consent)</font>

167
00:12:42,290 --> 00:12:45,790
<font color="yellow">I'll stamp on it on the day the bonds expire in six months.</font>

168
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:48,360
<font color="yellow">If you fail to help me then,</font>

169
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:51,390
<font color="yellow">I will not sign this agreement.</font>

170
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:54,360
<font color="yellow">That won't happen, so don't worry.</font>

171
00:12:57,190 --> 00:13:00,830
<font color="yellow">Also, don't come to the office to see me any more.</font>

172
00:13:01,530 --> 00:13:03,660
<font color="yellow">I'll tell you where to meet.</font>

173
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:06,360
<font color="yellow">Is it because of Soo Yeon?</font>

174
00:13:06,990 --> 00:13:08,160
<font color="yellow">Remember this.</font>

175
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:11,660
<font color="yellow">The moment she finds about us, we will no longer work together.</font>

176
00:13:14,830 --> 00:13:15,930
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

177
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:24,260
<font color="yellow">Your life will end up being ruined because of Soo Yeon.</font>

178
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,360
<font color="yellow">Come on in.</font>

179
00:13:36,890 --> 00:13:38,930
<font color="yellow">You were secretly waiting for us, right?</font>

180
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:40,790
<font color="yellow">Sit down, sit down.</font>

181
00:13:50,990 --> 00:13:51,990
<font color="yellow">Have some gimbap.</font>

182
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:54,460
<font color="yellow">You can't get me to talk even if you do this.</font>

183
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:55,940
<font color="yellow">Don't bother wasting your time.</font>

184
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:58,130
<font color="yellow">Dong Soo used to love gimbap.</font>

185
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:02,090
<font color="yellow">If I was making some, he'd be so busy...</font>

186
00:14:02,590 --> 00:14:03,860
<font color="yellow">stealing pieces beside me.</font>

187
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:07,430
<font color="yellow">I hate gimbap, so you two can eat it.</font>

188
00:14:09,430 --> 00:14:11,660
<font color="yellow">That's weird. Your mother said...</font>

189
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:13,360
<font color="yellow">that you like it.</font>

190
00:14:16,330 --> 00:14:17,460
<font color="yellow">My mother?</font>

191
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:21,060
<font color="yellow">These are from your mother back home.</font>

192
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:24,790
<font color="yellow">She told me you hate spinach and added burdock instead.</font>

193
00:14:25,530 --> 00:14:27,140
<font color="yellow">You met my mother?</font>

194
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:28,360
<font color="yellow">Don't worry.</font>

195
00:14:28,830 --> 00:14:32,900
<font color="yellow">I didn't mention that you kidnapped and murdered people.</font>

196
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:36,230
<font color="yellow">That would be a bad idea. She looked quite old.</font>

197
00:14:37,390 --> 00:14:40,490
<font color="yellow">She's old, but she worked so hard...</font>

198
00:14:40,490 --> 00:14:45,190
<font color="yellow">to make this gimbap for her son.</font>

199
00:14:45,930 --> 00:14:48,890
<font color="yellow">Her hands are wrinkly but still strong.</font>

200
00:14:49,330 --> 00:14:51,180
<font color="yellow">Why are you doing this to me?</font>

201
00:14:51,180 --> 00:14:52,990
<font color="yellow">You know very well why.</font>

202
00:14:53,330 --> 00:14:54,830
<font color="yellow">I didn't kill Dong Soo!</font>

203
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:56,560
<font color="yellow">I know. It was Il Jae.</font>

204
00:14:56,890 --> 00:14:59,130
<font color="yellow">Just tell me where the autopsy result is.</font>

205
00:14:59,130 --> 00:15:01,530
<font color="yellow">I don't know. I don't know! I said, I don't know!</font>

206
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:03,290
<font color="yellow">You'll remember it soon...</font>

207
00:15:03,660 --> 00:15:05,960
<font color="yellow">because I'll keep coming back until you do.</font>

208
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:07,330
<font color="yellow">Oh Soo Yeon.</font>

209
00:15:07,330 --> 00:15:11,230
<font color="yellow">Your mother still believes that you're a good son.</font>

210
00:15:11,890 --> 00:15:14,590
<font color="yellow">When I told her that you ended up here because of someone evil,</font>

211
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:17,790
<font color="yellow">she grabbed my hands and cried.</font>

212
00:15:20,630 --> 00:15:23,460
