424
00:27:14,990 --> 00:27:18,560
<font color="yellow">Don't you know the meaning of doing national tours?</font>

425
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:20,160
<font color="yellow">He needs to win the public over...</font>

426
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:22,790
<font color="yellow">by going around and acting as if he's on their side.</font>

427
00:27:22,790 --> 00:27:23,930
<font color="yellow">How can he give that up?</font>

428
00:27:23,930 --> 00:27:25,590
<font color="yellow">That only works if you have a lot of supporters.</font>

429
00:27:25,590 --> 00:27:27,860
<font color="yellow">You need to focus on reality instead of ideals.</font>

430
00:27:27,860 --> 00:27:29,730
<font color="yellow">What do you know about elections?</font>

431
00:27:29,730 --> 00:27:31,030
<font color="yellow">If you knew so well,</font>

432
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:33,730
<font color="yellow">why did you go to prison during your campaign?</font>

433
00:27:34,230 --> 00:27:35,260
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

434
00:27:35,630 --> 00:27:37,030
<font color="yellow">What did you just say?</font>

435
00:27:37,530 --> 00:27:40,090
<font color="yellow">We didn't come here to fight.</font>

436
00:27:41,290 --> 00:27:44,130
<font color="yellow">Tell me a realistic plan.</font>

437
00:27:45,090 --> 00:27:47,490
<font color="yellow">Enough with barking at each other.</font>

438
00:27:48,930 --> 00:27:50,730
<font color="yellow">I agree with the national tour.</font>

439
00:27:50,730 --> 00:27:53,660
<font color="yellow">I think that would be best to improve your public image.</font>

440
00:27:53,660 --> 00:27:55,820
<font color="yellow">Don't you know why his public image was ruined?</font>

441
00:27:55,820 --> 00:27:57,430
<font color="yellow">If it wasn't for the Seoul mayor scandal,</font>

442
00:27:57,430 --> 00:27:59,430
<font color="yellow">his rating wouldn't be so low!</font>

443
00:27:59,430 --> 00:28:00,730
<font color="yellow">Yeom Hyeong Gu!</font>

444
00:28:00,730 --> 00:28:02,060
<font color="yellow">I said, stop it.</font>

445
00:28:04,430 --> 00:28:08,190
<font color="yellow">What's your strategy then, Mr Yeom?</font>

446
00:28:09,030 --> 00:28:11,660
<font color="yellow">I'm trying to find out the weaknesses of the other candidates.</font>

447
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:14,460
<font color="yellow">We need to ruin their public image to make it easier for us.</font>

448
00:28:14,460 --> 00:28:17,060
<font color="yellow">That's an old and foolish strategy.</font>

449
00:28:17,060 --> 00:28:18,330
<font color="yellow">What do you mean it's old?</font>

450
00:28:18,330 --> 00:28:20,760
<font color="yellow">Don't you know you have to find the smallest faults in order...</font>

451
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:22,260
<font color="yellow">to win an election?</font>

452
00:28:22,260 --> 00:28:24,360
<font color="yellow">Do you think the other candidates will just sit still?</font>

453
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:27,060
<font color="yellow">If they do the same thing,</font>

454
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:29,230
<font color="yellow">we'll be at the most disadvantage.</font>

455
00:28:30,490 --> 00:28:33,390
<font color="yellow">I agree with Il Jae.</font>

456
00:28:35,790 --> 00:28:38,470
<font color="yellow">- Mr Yeom.
-  Yes, Sir.</font>

457
00:28:38,470 --> 00:28:39,890
<font color="yellow">Il Jae...</font>

458
00:28:40,730 --> 00:28:42,190
<font color="yellow">knows better about elections.</font>

459
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:45,530
<font color="yellow">You can step back...</font>

460
00:28:46,260 --> 00:28:48,590
<font color="yellow">- during the election.
-  I'm sorry?</font>

461
00:28:49,090 --> 00:28:50,760
<font color="yellow">But, Sir...</font>

462
00:28:52,060 --> 00:28:53,360
<font color="yellow">Il Jae.</font>

463
00:28:53,990 --> 00:28:56,260
<font color="yellow">Tell me your strategy.</font>

464
00:29:00,060 --> 00:29:02,360
<font color="yellow">You'll draw in votes if you put yourself down.</font>

465
00:29:02,760 --> 00:29:05,090
<font color="yellow">During the national campaign tour,</font>

466
00:29:05,090 --> 00:29:07,860
<font color="yellow">try to show yourself as the everyday Joe.</font>

467
00:29:07,860 --> 00:29:11,830
<font color="yellow">You should then meet with the shadow cabinet that were forgotten.</font>

468
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:13,030
<font color="yellow">After that...</font>

469
00:29:21,690 --> 00:29:23,030
<font color="yellow">You'll end up helping us.</font>

470
00:29:23,890 --> 00:29:27,160
<font color="yellow">You work so hard for Congressman Hwang,</font>

471
00:29:27,660 --> 00:29:29,460
<font color="yellow">but Il Jae will eat you alive.</font>

472
00:29:38,530 --> 00:29:40,260
<font color="yellow">He came here alone after meeting with Jae Man.</font>

473
00:29:42,090 --> 00:29:45,590
<font color="yellow">It's obvious there were disagreements during the meeting.</font>

474
00:30:01,630 --> 00:30:02,790
<font color="yellow">You better leave.</font>

475
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:06,260
<font color="yellow">I won't betray Congressman Hwang.</font>

476
00:30:06,260 --> 00:30:08,690
<font color="yellow">We didn't say anything about betraying him.</font>

477
00:30:09,430 --> 00:30:11,090
<font color="yellow">I only mentioned that you should get rid of Il Jae.</font>

478
00:30:13,190 --> 00:30:16,460
<font color="yellow">Just tell us where Il Jae's secret funds are going...</font>

479
00:30:16,460 --> 00:30:18,830
<font color="yellow">and give us the proof that he evaded taxes.</font>

480
00:30:18,830 --> 00:30:21,190
<font color="yellow">Then what about the election funds?</font>

481
00:30:21,190 --> 00:30:22,590
<font color="yellow">I'll take care of it, of course.</font>

482
00:30:23,190 --> 00:30:25,660
<font color="yellow">The thirsty will look for the well first.</font>

483
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:28,330
<font color="yellow">When they're in a financial problem after we get rid of Il Jae,</font>

484
00:30:28,860 --> 00:30:32,030
<font color="yellow">I'll decline Jae Man's request at first.</font>

485
00:30:32,030 --> 00:30:34,360
<font color="yellow">Then we'll act like you persuaded me.</font>

486
00:30:35,030 --> 00:30:37,530
<font color="yellow">That means you'll become the key figure to have made...</font>

487
00:30:38,090 --> 00:30:39,860
<font color="yellow">this campaign successful.</font>

488
00:30:44,690 --> 00:30:46,530
<font color="yellow">If Congressman Hwang becomes the president,</font>

489
00:30:48,630 --> 00:30:49,660
<font color="yellow">you'd become...</font>

490
00:30:50,790 --> 00:30:52,560
<font color="yellow">his right hand.</font>

491
00:30:53,690 --> 00:30:55,290
<font color="yellow">Of course, that's if Il Jae is gone.</font>

492
00:30:57,330 --> 00:30:58,490
<font color="yellow">By then,</font>

493
00:30:59,990 --> 00:31:02,800
<font color="yellow">Il Jae will be remarried to Ji Soo.</font>

494
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:04,160
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about that.</font>

495
00:31:05,430 --> 00:31:08,030
<font color="yellow">I'll make sure that doesn't happen.</font>

496
00:31:09,490 --> 00:31:11,660
<font color="yellow">You should tell him the details later.</font>

497
00:31:12,290 --> 00:31:13,760
<font color="yellow">Let me repeat.</font>

498
00:31:14,490 --> 00:31:17,190
<font color="yellow">My target is Il Jae, not Congressman Hwang.</font>

499
00:31:19,330 --> 00:31:20,690
<font color="yellow">I'll look into...</font>

500
00:31:22,460 --> 00:31:23,730
<font color="yellow">the documents you need.</font>

501
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:57,860
<font color="yellow">Did you wake up?</font>

502
00:31:58,690 --> 00:32:00,100
<font color="yellow">Mr Gong!</font>

503
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:01,260
<font color="yellow">Yes?</font>

504
00:32:02,490 --> 00:32:04,890
<font color="yellow">My legs...</font>

505
00:32:06,460 --> 00:32:07,830
<font color="yellow">I can't move them!</font>

506
00:32:07,830 --> 00:32:08,930
<font color="yellow">Pardon?</font>

507
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:13,090
<font color="yellow">Maybe you walked for too long earlier.</font>

508
00:32:13,090 --> 00:32:17,360
<font color="yellow">Are you sure I'm getting better?</font>

509
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:21,120
<font color="yellow">Dr Hwang says so. That's what we have to believe.</font>

510
00:32:21,120 --> 00:32:24,490
<font color="yellow">My paralysis is getting worse.</font>

511
00:32:25,390 --> 00:32:27,490
<font color="yellow">Could Dr Hwang...</font>

512
00:32:28,360 --> 00:32:31,030
<font color="yellow">be tricked by Gwi Ja?</font>

513
00:32:32,930 --> 00:32:35,260
<font color="yellow">I'll look into it.</font>

514
00:32:35,890 --> 00:32:38,290
<font color="yellow">No, don't bother.</font>

515
00:32:39,690 --> 00:32:41,690
<font color="yellow">Ask them for my medical records.</font>

516
00:32:43,290 --> 00:32:45,190
<font color="yellow">I better get checked...</font>

517
00:32:46,730 --> 00:32:48,000
<font color="yellow">by another doctor.</font>

518
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,460
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

519
00:33:04,630 --> 00:33:06,430
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

520
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:08,730
<font color="yellow">Why can't you show us the medical records?</font>

521
00:33:09,430 --> 00:33:11,390
<font color="yellow">The thing is...</font>

522
00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:15,230
<font color="yellow">I told him not to reveal it.</font>

523
00:33:18,330 --> 00:33:20,950
<font color="yellow">Could you give us a moment?</font>

524
00:33:20,950 --> 00:33:21,990
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

525
00:33:29,530 --> 00:33:31,790
<font color="yellow">Mr Gong, listen to me carefully.</font>

526
00:33:32,760 --> 00:33:36,790
<font color="yellow">Father is terminally ill.</font>

527
00:33:37,330 --> 00:33:38,630
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

528
00:33:40,090 --> 00:33:41,430
<font color="yellow">He's terminally ill?</font>

529
00:33:41,860 --> 00:33:43,520
<font color="yellow">He has less than six months.</font>

530
00:33:43,520 --> 00:33:46,460
<font color="yellow">It's best not to tell him.</font>

531
00:33:46,460 --> 00:33:48,160
<font color="yellow">Is there no hope?</font>

532
00:33:49,190 --> 00:33:51,160
<font color="yellow">Can't he have surgery?</font>

533
00:33:52,460 --> 00:33:53,530
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

534
00:33:54,530 --> 00:33:56,830
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you tell me before?</font>

535
00:33:57,260 --> 00:34:00,190
<font color="yellow">I couldn't tell you because the results weren't out.</font>

536
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:04,690
<font color="yellow">We better tell his family.</font>

537
00:34:04,690 --> 00:34:06,660
<font color="yellow">- We can't do that.
-  What do you mean?</font>

538
00:34:07,290 --> 00:34:11,160
<font color="yellow">Are you going to let him die alone like that?</font>

539
00:34:11,160 --> 00:34:13,330
<font color="yellow">Don't you know why he ended up like that?</font>

540
00:34:13,330 --> 00:34:15,890
<font color="yellow">Those people are not his family.</font>

541
00:34:16,630 --> 00:34:17,990
<font color="yellow">I won't forgive them.</font>

542
00:34:17,990 --> 00:34:21,110
<font color="yellow">We should at least tell Shin Young.</font>

543
00:34:21,110 --> 00:34:22,730
<font color="yellow">I'll tell her myself.</font>

544
00:34:23,230 --> 00:34:27,360
<font color="yellow">Please focus on making Father as comfortable as he can be.</font>

545
00:34:32,830 --> 00:34:33,860
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

546
00:34:35,330 --> 00:34:38,190
<font color="yellow">Chairman Do has disappeared again.</font>

547
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:41,230
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about? What do you mean he disappeared?</font>

548
00:34:47,890 --> 00:34:51,460
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. He was gone when I came back from the washroom.</font>

549
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:57,190
<font color="yellow">If he got changed, maybe he went to Congressman Hwang's again.</font>

550
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:06,430
<font color="yellow">- Sir.
-  Have you checked the CCTV?</font>

551
00:35:06,430 --> 00:35:10,230
<font color="yellow">He was picking flowers in the garden an hour ago.</font>

552
00:35:10,230 --> 00:35:11,290
<font color="yellow">Flowers?</font>

553
00:35:11,690 --> 00:35:12,960
<font color="yellow">That must be it.</font>

554
00:35:13,630 --> 00:35:16,690
<font color="yellow">He went to find his wife.</font>

555
00:35:31,290 --> 00:35:32,290
<font color="yellow">Gwi Ja.</font>

556
00:35:33,290 --> 00:35:36,160
<font color="yellow">These are for you.</font>

557
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:42,310
<font color="yellow">Take the flowers...</font>

558
00:35:42,310 --> 00:35:43,660
<font color="yellow">before his arms fall off.</font>

559
00:35:48,430 --> 00:35:50,330
<font color="yellow">You're so generous.</font>

560
00:35:50,330 --> 00:35:51,360
<font color="yellow">Jae Man.</font>

561
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:53,360
<font color="yellow">Give me...</font>

562
00:35:54,060 --> 00:35:55,630
<font color="yellow">Gwi Ja's hand.</font>

563
00:35:56,630 --> 00:35:57,630
<font color="yellow">I want...</font>

564
00:35:59,030 --> 00:36:00,260
<font color="yellow">to marry her.</font>

565
00:36:00,630 --> 00:36:02,330
<font color="yellow">Oh dear...</font>

566
00:36:02,890 --> 00:36:03,890
<font color="yellow">I know...</font>

567
00:36:04,890 --> 00:36:06,460
<font color="yellow">you don't like me.</font>

568
00:36:07,590 --> 00:36:08,630
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

569
00:36:09,990 --> 00:36:12,090
<font color="yellow">I'm sure I can...</font>

570
00:36:12,490 --> 00:36:13,630
<font color="yellow">make her happy.</font>

571
00:36:16,590 --> 00:36:19,030
<font color="yellow">How will you make her happy?</font>

572
00:36:21,890 --> 00:36:22,960
<font color="yellow">Right now,</font>

573
00:36:24,230 --> 00:36:25,260
<font color="yellow">I am penniless.</font>

574
00:36:26,490 --> 00:36:27,530
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

575
00:36:28,990 --> 00:36:30,590
<font color="yellow">I'll make sure...</font>

576
00:36:32,160 --> 00:36:34,330
<font color="yellow">you can live a luxurious life.</font>

577
00:36:35,060 --> 00:36:38,360
<font color="yellow">Was this what he was like?</font>

578
00:36:39,990 --> 00:36:40,990
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

579
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:43,290
<font color="yellow">But who cares?</font>

580
00:36:44,530 --> 00:36:46,630
<font color="yellow">We're practically enemies now.</font>

581
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:49,090
<font color="yellow">I'm hungry.</font>

582
00:36:50,430 --> 00:36:51,430
<font color="yellow">Gwi Ja.</font>

583
00:36:52,260 --> 00:36:54,230
<font color="yellow">I'd like a chicken...</font>

584
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:57,330
<font color="yellow">your mother cooked for me.</font>

585
00:37:01,490 --> 00:37:03,690
<font color="yellow">Tell Shin Young to come right over.</font>

586
00:37:04,430 --> 00:37:06,390
<font color="yellow">What for?</font>

587
00:37:06,830 --> 00:37:09,660
<font color="yellow">I need her permission to look after your dad.</font>

588
00:37:10,660 --> 00:37:11,730
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

589
00:37:31,230 --> 00:37:32,510
<font color="yellow">He came over...</font>

590
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:35,460
<font color="yellow">with the flowers to propose to Mum.</font>

591
00:37:38,090 --> 00:37:40,260
<font color="yellow">Dad, come with me.</font>

592
00:37:40,590 --> 00:37:41,860
<font color="yellow">I'll look after you.</font>

593
00:37:45,730 --> 00:37:46,730
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

594
00:37:47,530 --> 00:37:50,500
<font color="yellow">I'm Shin Young, your daughter.</font>

595
00:37:50,500 --> 00:37:51,530
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

596
00:37:52,830 --> 00:37:55,990
<font color="yellow">I'll marry Gwi Ja and live here.</font>

597
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:01,560
<font color="yellow">He's gotten worse.</font>

598
00:38:05,230 --> 00:38:07,760
<font color="yellow">I think it's best for him...</font>

599
00:38:08,130 --> 00:38:10,430
<font color="yellow">if we look after him.</font>

600
00:38:10,890 --> 00:38:12,430
<font color="yellow">Be good to him.</font>

601
00:38:14,030 --> 00:38:15,760
<font color="yellow">If he makes one complaint,</font>

602
00:38:16,430 --> 00:38:17,830
<font color="yellow">I'll come for him.</font>

603
00:38:20,890 --> 00:38:21,930
<font color="yellow">Are you leaving already?</font>

604
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:26,530
<font color="yellow">Don't just sit there. Get up.</font>

605
00:38:26,530 --> 00:38:28,530
<font color="yellow">What? Right.</font>

606
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:38,060
<font color="yellow">They're likely to inherit his assets if he stays here.</font>

607
00:38:38,430 --> 00:38:41,160
<font color="yellow">He's practically a blessing to them.</font>

608
00:38:41,860 --> 00:38:44,660
<font color="yellow">Have some, Mr Hwang.</font>

609
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:49,730
<font color="yellow">I'm fine. The chicken's all yours.</font>

610
00:38:50,260 --> 00:38:53,030
<font color="yellow">He thinks you're his father-in-law.</font>

611
00:38:53,860 --> 00:38:55,530
<font color="yellow">I think his memory...</font>

612
00:38:55,990 --> 00:38:58,490
<font color="yellow">is going back in time.</font>

613
00:38:59,490 --> 00:39:00,530
<font color="yellow">He might end up...</font>

614
00:39:01,330 --> 00:39:03,960
<font color="yellow">asking for a bottle of milk.</font>

615
00:39:10,330 --> 00:39:12,690
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about him and focus on work.</font>

616
00:39:17,890 --> 00:39:18,960
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

617
00:39:19,430 --> 00:39:20,770
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

618
00:39:20,770 --> 00:39:22,220
<font color="yellow">I know my father's here.</font>

619
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:23,410
<font color="yellow">So what?</font>

620
00:39:23,410 --> 00:39:24,690
<font color="yellow">I'll take him with me.</font>

621
00:39:25,230 --> 00:39:27,000
<font color="yellow">You're so brazen.</font>

622
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:29,090
<font color="yellow">Don't you know I'm his legal custodian?</font>

623
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:31,190
<font color="yellow">He won't live...</font>

624
00:39:32,630 --> 00:39:33,690
<font color="yellow">much longer.</font>

625
00:39:34,860 --> 00:39:36,030
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

626
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:40,360
<font color="yellow">He is terminally ill and dying.</font>

627
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:43,230
<font color="yellow">What do you mean he's terminally ill?</font>

628
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:46,560
<font color="yellow">Are you saying he'll die soon?</font>

629
00:39:47,490 --> 00:39:49,130
<font color="yellow">He has less than six months left.</font>

630
00:39:51,230 --> 00:39:54,230
<font color="yellow">I can't let him spend the rest of his life with these people.</font>

631
00:39:54,230 --> 00:39:55,760
<font color="yellow">Let me take care of him.</font>

632
00:39:56,130 --> 00:39:57,360
<font color="yellow">This mess...</font>

633
00:39:58,630 --> 00:40:00,510
<font color="yellow">only happened because of you.</font>

634
00:40:00,510 --> 00:40:02,030
<font color="yellow">- Shin Young.
-  Get lost.</font>

635
00:40:03,130 --> 00:40:05,060
<font color="yellow">You'll never see our dad again.</font>

636
00:40:05,690 --> 00:40:06,690
<font color="yellow">Never.</font>

637
00:40:32,890 --> 00:40:33,920
<font color="yellow">Thanks for coming.</font>

638
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:36,690
<font color="yellow">I can't refuse my boss' call.</font>

639
00:40:37,990 --> 00:40:39,630
