<font color="yellow">Call a family meeting.</font>

856
00:55:35,730 --> 00:55:37,360
<font color="yellow">What's the use of that?</font>

857
00:55:37,790 --> 00:55:39,490
<font color="yellow">They'll all object.</font>

858
00:55:39,490 --> 00:55:41,830
<font color="yellow">If something happens to him during surgery,</font>

859
00:55:42,490 --> 00:55:44,130
<font color="yellow">they'll hold you responsible.</font>

860
00:55:44,790 --> 00:55:47,690
<font color="yellow">Mr Gong's right. Call a family meeting.</font>

861
00:55:52,590 --> 00:55:54,590
<font color="yellow">Bring my father over here...</font>

862
00:55:55,790 --> 00:55:57,160
<font color="yellow">and call a meeting.</font>

863
00:56:15,990 --> 00:56:17,680
<font color="yellow">It's been a while, Soo Yeon.</font>

864
00:56:17,680 --> 00:56:19,060
<font color="yellow">Come with me.</font>

865
00:56:38,990 --> 00:56:39,990
<font color="yellow">Bok Shin.</font>

866
00:56:41,360 --> 00:56:42,450
<font color="yellow">Where am I?</font>

867
00:56:42,450 --> 00:56:43,460
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

868
00:56:44,590 --> 00:56:45,890
<font color="yellow">Do you feel better?</font>

869
00:56:46,490 --> 00:56:47,830
<font color="yellow">Why am I here?</font>

870
00:56:48,390 --> 00:56:50,090
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

871
00:56:51,790 --> 00:56:52,790
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

872
00:56:53,460 --> 00:56:54,490
<font color="yellow">I need you...</font>

873
00:56:56,490 --> 00:56:58,330
<font color="yellow">to listen very carefully.</font>

874
00:57:08,330 --> 00:57:10,660
<font color="yellow">The chairman will join you shortly.</font>

875
00:57:15,490 --> 00:57:17,790
<font color="yellow">Why do we need a meeting?</font>

876
00:57:18,630 --> 00:57:19,660
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

877
00:57:20,360 --> 00:57:22,580
<font color="yellow">Shin Young's all grown up.</font>

878
00:57:22,580 --> 00:57:24,460
<font color="yellow">Just one word from her...</font>

879
00:57:24,460 --> 00:57:27,260
<font color="yellow">and even Gun Woo came running.</font>

880
00:57:27,990 --> 00:57:31,130
<font color="yellow">He's here for a reason. Money.</font>

881
00:57:32,590 --> 00:57:35,830
<font color="yellow">Just look at him. He even brought his lawyer.</font>

882
00:57:35,830 --> 00:57:37,340
<font color="yellow">Watch your manners.</font>

883
00:57:37,340 --> 00:57:38,730
<font color="yellow">There are other people here.</font>

884
00:57:39,090 --> 00:57:40,090
<font color="yellow">Who?</font>

885
00:57:40,530 --> 00:57:41,530
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon?</font>

886
00:57:42,530 --> 00:57:45,790
<font color="yellow">She might be special to you, but do we have to be polite?</font>

887
00:57:49,190 --> 00:57:50,190
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

888
00:57:50,530 --> 00:57:51,990
<font color="yellow">Don't you think...</font>

889
00:57:51,990 --> 00:57:56,230
<font color="yellow">Shin Young's too arrogant just because she's Dad's custodian?</font>

890
00:57:56,230 --> 00:57:59,890
<font color="yellow">She'll be a nobody once he dies.</font>

891
00:58:06,590 --> 00:58:07,860
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

892
00:58:13,990 --> 00:58:14,990
<font color="yellow">Dad.</font>

893
00:58:19,890 --> 00:58:22,830
<font color="yellow">Why isn't he responding?</font>

894
00:58:27,890 --> 00:58:29,570
<font color="yellow">Do you want...</font>

895
00:58:29,570 --> 00:58:32,320
<font color="yellow">to keep it a secret from Shin Young, too?</font>

896
00:58:32,320 --> 00:58:33,330
<font color="yellow">I don't know...</font>

897
00:58:34,460 --> 00:58:35,890
<font color="yellow">whom exactly...</font>

898
00:58:37,390 --> 00:58:38,430
<font color="yellow">I can trust.</font>

899
00:58:39,360 --> 00:58:41,590
<font color="yellow">Who is really on my side?</font>

900
00:58:42,690 --> 00:58:45,030
<font color="yellow">I need to find that out.</font>

901
00:58:48,790 --> 00:58:50,830
<font color="yellow">He can't speak...</font>

902
00:58:51,290 --> 00:58:52,790
<font color="yellow">or understand a word.</font>

903
00:58:55,430 --> 00:58:56,460
<font color="yellow">Don't worry.</font>

904
00:58:57,230 --> 00:58:58,260
<font color="yellow">I will...</font>

905
00:58:58,860 --> 00:59:00,190
<font color="yellow">make you better.</font>

906
00:59:02,630 --> 00:59:03,790
<font color="yellow">Let's take him outside.</font>

907
00:59:31,160 --> 00:59:34,490
<font color="yellow">I gathered you here to make an important announcement.</font>

908
00:59:35,590 --> 00:59:37,130
<font color="yellow">What announcement?</font>

909
00:59:37,630 --> 00:59:39,580
<font color="yellow">You called a lawyer.</font>

910
00:59:39,580 --> 00:59:41,830
<font color="yellow">Is this about the inheritance?</font>

911
00:59:43,730 --> 00:59:47,530
<font color="yellow">There's a possibility that surgery will cure Dad completely.</font>

912
00:59:51,360 --> 00:59:53,760
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

913
00:59:53,760 --> 00:59:54,790
<font color="yellow">Your dad...</font>

914
00:59:55,190 --> 00:59:56,680
<font color="yellow">was terminal.</font>

915
00:59:56,680 --> 00:59:58,360
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo lied.</font>

916
01:00:00,160 --> 01:00:01,160
<font color="yellow">Did you...</font>

917
01:00:01,590 --> 01:00:02,950
<font color="yellow">check your facts?</font>

918
01:00:02,950 --> 01:00:05,260
<font color="yellow">The success rate is 10 percent.</font>

919
01:00:05,260 --> 01:00:07,440
<font color="yellow">That means there's a 90-percent chance he'll die.</font>

920
01:00:07,440 --> 01:00:09,720
<font color="yellow">No doctor in Korea can operate on him.</font>

921
01:00:09,720 --> 01:00:12,330
<font color="yellow">Doctor Campbell will be flown in from America.</font>

922
01:00:13,690 --> 01:00:14,690
<font color="yellow">He's...</font>

923
01:00:15,260 --> 01:00:16,930
<font color="yellow">an expert in brain surgery.</font>

924
01:00:17,590 --> 01:00:19,150
<font color="yellow">Did you put her up to this?</font>

925
01:00:19,150 --> 01:00:20,690
<font color="yellow">It's not wrong to want...</font>

926
01:00:21,330 --> 01:00:22,460
<font color="yellow">the chairman to live.</font>

927
01:00:22,960 --> 01:00:25,860
<font color="yellow">Why won't you get rid of the bullet in your head?</font>

928
01:00:25,860 --> 01:00:28,490
<font color="yellow">You're afraid the surgery will kill you.</font>

929
01:00:28,990 --> 01:00:31,330
<font color="yellow">You can't subject my father to this.</font>

930
01:00:31,330 --> 01:00:33,560
<font color="yellow">The success rate of my surgery is zero.</font>

931
01:00:34,790 --> 01:00:35,790
<font color="yellow">It's zero percent.</font>

932
01:00:39,260 --> 01:00:41,390
<font color="yellow">If any doctor had given me a 10-percent success rate,</font>

933
01:00:42,190 --> 01:00:44,590
<font color="yellow">I'd have done it if only to get back...</font>

934
01:00:45,690 --> 01:00:47,090
<font color="yellow">the memories I lost.</font>

935
01:00:52,460 --> 01:00:53,460
<font color="yellow">This morning,</font>

936
01:00:53,790 --> 01:00:55,390
<font color="yellow">I spoke with Doctor Campbell.</font>

937
01:00:55,990 --> 01:00:57,730
<font color="yellow">The success rate isn't 10 percent.</font>

938
01:00:59,060 --> 01:01:01,160
<font color="yellow">It's over 30 percent.</font>

939
01:01:07,330 --> 01:01:08,330
<font color="yellow">I'm...</font>

940
01:01:08,960 --> 01:01:10,390
<font color="yellow">I'm against it.</font>

941
01:01:11,530 --> 01:01:12,890
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

942
01:01:13,360 --> 01:01:15,460
<font color="yellow">The 30-percent success rate means...</font>

943
01:01:16,460 --> 01:01:18,580
<font color="yellow">there's a 70-percent chance it will fail.</font>

944
01:01:18,580 --> 01:01:19,590
<font color="yellow">Then...</font>

945
01:01:20,060 --> 01:01:21,930
<font color="yellow">do you want to let him die?</font>

946
01:01:23,790 --> 01:01:25,890
<font color="yellow">It's not my place to say, but...</font>

947
01:01:27,390 --> 01:01:29,160
<font color="yellow">since you're all here,</font>

948
01:01:30,230 --> 01:01:31,390
<font color="yellow">put it to a vote.</font>

949
01:01:33,860 --> 01:01:35,460
<font color="yellow">Whoever is against the surgery,</font>

950
01:01:37,090 --> 01:01:38,160
<font color="yellow">raise your hand.</font>

951
01:01:50,090 --> 01:01:51,430
<font color="yellow">Other than Shin Young,</font>

952
01:01:52,530 --> 01:01:54,330
<font color="yellow">everyone objects.</font>

953
01:01:55,430 --> 01:01:56,430
<font color="yellow">The surgery...</font>

954
01:01:56,990 --> 01:01:58,560
<font color="yellow">will not happen.</font>

955
01:02:00,730 --> 01:02:02,290
<font color="yellow">I'm his custodian.</font>

956
01:02:02,730 --> 01:02:03,730
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh.</font>

957
01:02:04,290 --> 01:02:07,060
<font color="yellow">The others don't have a legal say, do they?</font>

958
01:02:08,290 --> 01:02:10,430
<font color="yellow">No. They don't.</font>

959
01:02:10,430 --> 01:02:12,450
<font color="yellow">I don't care what you say.</font>

960
01:02:12,450 --> 01:02:13,460
<font color="yellow">I called you here...</font>

961
01:02:13,860 --> 01:02:16,050
<font color="yellow">to tell you that he's getting the surgery.</font>

962
01:02:16,050 --> 01:02:18,430
<font color="yellow">When did you start caring about him?</font>

963
01:02:18,430 --> 01:02:20,990
<font color="yellow">He said he'd give you half of his assets.</font>

964
01:02:20,990 --> 01:02:22,460
<font color="yellow">That's what this is about!</font>

965
01:02:22,460 --> 01:02:25,330
<font color="yellow">Are you going to kill Dad to take his money?</font>

966
01:02:25,730 --> 01:02:27,660
<font color="yellow">Why are you against the surgery?</font>

967
01:02:28,060 --> 01:02:31,450
<font color="yellow">You're afraid he'll recover and you'll end up without a penny!</font>

968
01:02:31,450 --> 01:02:34,350
<font color="yellow">Learn to give up when everyone says no.</font>

969
01:02:34,350 --> 01:02:36,220
<font color="yellow">What are you even doing here?</font>

970
01:02:36,220 --> 01:02:37,260
<font color="yellow">What do you think?</font>

971
01:02:37,590 --> 01:02:40,960
<font color="yellow">Don't you know my dad's the reason your family's so rich?</font>

972
01:02:40,960 --> 01:02:42,560
<font color="yellow">We own shares.</font>

973
01:02:43,330 --> 01:02:44,490
<font color="yellow">Stop it, all of you.</font>

974
01:02:45,090 --> 01:02:46,950
<font color="yellow">What would Soo Yeon think of us?</font>

975
01:02:46,950 --> 01:02:49,730
<font color="yellow">Don't act like you're so blameless.</font>

976
01:02:49,730 --> 01:02:53,460
<font color="yellow">You told us Dad was terminally ill because you were up to something!</font>

977
01:02:53,460 --> 01:02:56,090
<font color="yellow">I've had enough. Shut your mouth.</font>

978
01:02:56,090 --> 01:02:58,790
<font color="yellow">This is how I talk! It can't be helped!</font>

979
01:02:58,790 --> 01:03:00,190
<font color="yellow">May you all...</font>

980
01:03:01,390 --> 01:03:03,890
<font color="yellow">be struck by lightning!</font>

981
01:03:30,630 --> 01:03:32,430
<font color="yellow">(Monster)</font>

982
01:03:32,960 --> 01:03:34,730
<font color="yellow">Do Choong's secret safe?</font>

983
01:03:34,730 --> 01:03:38,090
<font color="yellow">I might be able to find proof that Il Jae killed your parents.</font>

984
01:03:38,090 --> 01:03:39,460
<font color="yellow">Don't visit me any more.</font>

985
01:03:39,460 --> 01:03:41,390
<font color="yellow">Are you going to betray me, too?</font>

986
01:03:41,390 --> 01:03:43,350
<font color="yellow">Look after Shin Young for me.</font>

987
01:03:43,350 --> 01:03:45,860
<font color="yellow">He died at 9:28am.</font>

988
01:03:45,860 --> 01:03:49,190
<font color="yellow">If the surgery's a success, it puts a dent in my plan.</font>

989
01:03:49,190 --> 01:03:50,460
<font color="yellow">He's already dead.</font>

990
01:03:50,460 --> 01:03:52,290
<font color="yellow">This dirty fight will end.</font>

991
01:03:52,290 --> 01:03:54,690
<font color="yellow">I won't die until I get what I want.</font>

